<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
 <title>last radio control should be checked when "checked" attribute is set for the whole group</title>
 <style>
  span { display:block; height:2em; width:2em; background:red }
  input { display:none }
  input:default + span { background:lime }
  input:checked + span { background:red }
  input#i3:default + span { background:red }
  input#i3:default:checked + span { background:lime }
 </style>
 <p>There should be three green squares below:</p>
 <p><input type="radio" name="test" checked="checked"/><span/></p>
 <p><input type="radio" name="test" checked="checked"/><span/></p>
 <p><input type="radio" name="test" checked="checked" id="i3"/><span/></p>
</html>